		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Poe Ballantine</span></strong>&rsquo;s latest book of essays is <em>501 Minutes to Christ</em> (Hawthorne Books). He lives in Chadron, Nebraska, and writes: &ldquo;I&rsquo;ve cut the fingers off all my gloves for better warming over trash-can fires, and I&rsquo;m working on several recipes for mulligan stew &shy;&mdash; with and without dumpster tomatoes.&rdquo;</p><a href="/contributors/poe-ballantine" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
